        <div class="headline row columns text-center">
          <div class="small-12 medium-6 column">
            <h3 class="font-color-dark text-left">What is Machine Intelligence and Why Leaf?</h3>
            <p class="text-left font-color-dark">
              Machine Intelligence designs algorithms with which machines can
              learn something about their environment from data. These machines
              are then able to solve complex and often narrow problems very
              efficently.<br/>
              Leaf and Autumn's platform provide the tools to create these
              Machine Intelligence applications. As current hardware is just
              sufficient enough to make the Machine Intelligence algorithms for
              real-world problems practical, Leaf provides the interface to run
              these algorithms on a most effective way. Leaf is a flexible,
              modular and portable Framework for numeric computations and can
              therefore be used for many powerfull Machine Intelligence paradigms,
              not only e.g. Deep Learning. We embrace Rust, a language which is
              very well suited for current state-of-the-art and future Machine
              Intelligence. It allows for the performance,
              memory-security, and extensibility, that other frameworks
              (TensorFlow, Caffe, Theano) only gain by combining high-level
              languages (Python) with low-level languages (C, C++).
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="small-12 medium-6 column">
            <div class="quote-wrapper row">
              <div class="small-2 large-2 columns testimonial">
                <div class="quote-marks">&#8220;</div>
