              <div class="small-10 large-10 columns testimonial">
                <div class="quote">
                  <p class="font-color-dark">
                  The design of Leaf was influenced by the brilliant people behind
                  Caffe, Tensorflow, Rust and numerous reasearch papers. With Leaf
